Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 07 of Mamma MRI
When I select the radio button 'Mass'
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled
And 'Max. axial diameter' input field is enabled
And 'Pleura' checkbox is enabled
And 'Pericardium' checkbox is enabled
And 'Bones' checkbox is enabled
And 'Mediastinum' checkbox is enabled
And 'Suspected' checkbox is enabled
And 'Consolidation' radio button is enabled
And 'Atelectasis' radio button is enabled
When I check 'Left' checkbox
And I select '20' in 'Max. axial diameter' input field
And I check 'Pleura' checkbox
And I check 'Pericardium' checkbox
And I check 'Bones' checkbox
And I check 'Mediastinum' checkbox
And I check 'Suspected' checkbox
And I select 'Atelectasis' radio button
And I click on 'Next page' button
Then I'm redirected to Page 08 of Mamma MRI
